Key Match Events: Nurul Hasan Sohan collected the ball ahead of stumps resulting in a no ball and a free hit.
Blessing Muzarabani missed the final ball, resulting in Bangladesh's win.
Richard Ngarava hit a six but was dismissed shortly after.
Bradley Evans was caught out by Afif at deep mid-wicket.
Shakib Al Hasan executed an incredible run-out to dismiss Sean Williams, who scored 64 off 42 balls.
